  "title": "feat(toggle): Provide a better default widget",
  "body": "This update brings:\n- default to showing the next user action items count instead of the\n  current number of displayed hits\n\nwhich means:\nif checkbox is not checked, show: [ ] free shipping (countWhenChecked)\nif checkbox is checked, show: [x] free shipping (countWhenNotChecked)\n- fix numeric based on and off values (fixes #1096)\n- provide `onFacetValue` and `offFacetValue` template data, fixes #919\n",
